  <title>Assessment of the Genetic Diversity of Xanthomonas axonopodis pv. phaseoli and Xanthomonas fuscans subsp. fuscans as a Basis To Identify Putative Pathogenicity Genes and a Type III Secretion System of the SPI-1 Family by Multiple Suppression Subtractive Hybridizations</title>
